00:00:11.247 --> 00:00:12.764
KEITH: Hi, everybody.

00:00:12.764 --> 00:00:14.055
My name is Keith [? Schafer ?].

00:00:14.055 --> 00:00:17.782
I'm with the author's team
here at Google Los Angeles.

00:00:17.782 --> 00:00:20.100
