SUSAN PINKER: Praise.

00:30:01.530 --> 00:30:02.610
You guys are amazing.

00:30:02.610 --> 00:30:04.590
No wonder you work here.

00:30:04.590 --> 00:30:06.410
It's very, very
interesting answers.

00:30:06.410 --> 00:30:10.331
Well, let's look at
some of the evidence.

00:30:10.331 --> 00:30:13.970
Is it quality of parenting?

00:30:13.970 --> 00:30:17.090
And this is a cartoon that
says, and then Winnie the Pooh

00:30:17.090 --> 00:30:19.315
decided it was time to
